          <actionDate>2019-01-03</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Universal Right to Vote by Mail Act of 2019 </strong></p> <p> This bill prohibits a state from imposing additional conditions or requirements on the eligibility of an individual to cast a vote in federal elections by mail, except to the extent that it imposes a deadline for requesting the ballot and returning it to the appropriate state or local election official.</p>]]></text>
